      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（それは麻奈が事故で亡くなって）\n（しばらく経ってからのことだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(This is something that happened)\n(a while after Mana died in her accident.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.2666666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "……くん、{user}君？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey… {user}? Are you listening?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.366666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "お茶、もう下げてもいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you mind if I clear the tea?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……すみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… Thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.504920450846353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君\n元気だよ、元気！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously‚ {user}.\nCheer up! Smile!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.777322546641027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……ちょっと、外、出てきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going out for a little bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.955305894215897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 20.138639227549227
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "…………はぁ\nこんなんじゃダメだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*\nI can’t go on like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.221972560882566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 26.333333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_flashback-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 26.55530589421594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、{user}くん\n手、繋いでもいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}.\nCan we hold hands?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈のことを吹っ切らないと……）\n（麻奈だって、前に進んでほしいと思っているはずだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I need to get over Mana.)\n(I’m sure she would want me to move on.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 40.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（俺は必死にその方法を探した。お墓に行って）\n（麻奈に語りかけ、事故現場に行って現実を胸に刻む）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I desperately searched for a way. I went to her grave‚ talked to her‚)\n(went to the scene of the accident to etch the truth into my heart.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage04",
      "startTime": 51.06666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage04",
      "startTime": 51.06666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "行ってくるよ、{user}くん\nそこから、見守っててね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll be right back‚ {user}.\nWatch over me‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（グランプリの決勝の会場にも行った）\n（けど、やっぱりダメだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I even went to the venue where the Grand Prix finals were supposed to be held.)\n(But… nothing worked.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 63.45
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あと残っているのは……\n……そうか……まだ一つ、行っていない場所があった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s only one thing left…\nThat’s right. There’s still one place I haven’t been to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage05",
      "startTime": 74.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（母校の高校は卒業した時と変わらずそこにあった）\n（職員室で許可を取った俺は見学させてもらうことにした）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(My alma mater was just as it was the day we graduated.)\n(I got permission from the faculty to explore the campus.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage06",
      "startTime": 85.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage06",
      "startTime": 85.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "とてもワガママでメチャクチャなお願いだから\n嫌だったら、嫌って言って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ well‚ it’s a crazy and selfish request.\nIf you don’t like the idea‚ just turn me down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈に初めて声をかけられた教室）\n（あそこに行けば、何かふっ切れるような気がした）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The classroom where Mana first spoke to me.)\n(If I went there‚ I felt I could get some sort of closure.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage08",
      "startTime": 100.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage08",
      "startTime": 100.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "…………なんにも変わってないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nothing’s changed at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……えっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "こら。聞こえない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey. Can’t you hear me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage08",
      "startTime": 109.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……麻奈？\nいやいや、幻聴だ。そんなはず……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana?\nNo‚ no. I’m just hearing things. It can’t be…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage08",
      "startTime": 118.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈がかつて座っていた席を見る）\n（するとそこに麻奈がいた。あの時と変わらない笑顔で）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I look at the desk where Mana once sat.)\n(And there was Mana. Smiling the same way she did that day.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "何、びっくりしてるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you startled?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 124.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage08",
      "startTime": 127.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "（これは夢だ。夢に決まっている。麻奈が）\n（いなくなってから、何度も何度も何度も見た夢だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(This is a dream. It has to be a dream.)\n(It’s the same dream I saw over and over ever since she died.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage08",
      "startTime": 135.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "（自分の頬を叩いて、さらにつねる）\n（でも、今度は目覚めなかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I slap my cheeks and pinch myself for good measure.)\n(But this time‚ I don’t wake up.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_01-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "……久しぶりね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s been a while.",
